PROBLEM TITLE : Kth Smallest
PROBLEM DIFFICULTY : Medium
PLATFORM NAME : GeeksForGeeks
PROBLEM LINK : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/kth-smallest-element5635/1
SOLUTION : 

class Solution 
{
    public static int kthSmallest(int[] arr, int k) 
    {
        Arrays.sort(arr);
        return arr[k-1];
    }
}

APPROACH :
First, we'll sort the array.
Then, we'll return the element at the Kth-1 index.
